43:49.156 --> 43:49.937
Hello?

43:50.197 --> 43:53.281
It's Johnson's phrase, as you know.

43:53.341 --> 43:54.923
It's Johnson's phrase?

43:55.163 --> 43:55.243
Yes.

43:55.263 --> 44:05.195
