48:02.935 --> 48:04.357
That's his great work.

48:05.759 --> 48:07.081
And it's hard to match that.

48:08.543 --> 48:13.631
You anoint him the American Goethe, too, which I find very interesting.

48:13.651 --> 48:14.231
Oh, yes, yes.

48:14.392 --> 48:16.414
I think he is the national sage.

48:17.376 --> 48:18.197
No sin.

48:18.953 --> 48:24.362
You know what, Harold, I'm going to let you go because this must get firing.

48:25.043 --> 48:26.986
Well, it's a great pleasure.

48:27.026 --> 48:29.831
We're actually at the point we had agreed on anyway.

48:29.871 --> 48:30.852
We've done 45 minutes.

48:31.133 --> 48:34.158
