48:34.178 --> 48:34.538
Thank you.

48:34.578 --> 48:35.099
Thank you.

48:35.119 --> 48:36.622
And thank you so much for everything.

48:36.722 --> 48:38.465
Nick, prosper, please.

48:38.485 --> 48:38.946
Thank you, sir.

48:38.986 --> 48:39.326
You too.

48:39.366 --> 48:40.468
Take good care of your health.

48:40.528 --> 48:41.790
Thank you, sir.

48:44.615 --> 48:44.775
Bye-bye.

